<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(فَرْعٌ)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">فِي الْكِتَابِ:</span> تَجُوزُ فِي الِاحْتِطَابِ وَالِاحْتِشَاشِ وَأَنْ يَحْمِلَا عَلَى رِقَابِهِمَا ثمار<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>